{"text": "## Feeding your baby\n\n\n Breastfeeding is the safest way to feed an infant during emergencies. For infants who are not breastfeeding or being fed breast milk, ready-to-feed infant formula is the next safest option.\n\n When powdered infant formula is the only option, use bottled water or boiled tap water to prepare formula until officials say your tap water is safe to drink.\n\n Always clean infant feeding items with bottled, boiled, or treated water and soap before each use", "embedding": [0.030294754, 0.032608557, -0.15569203, -0.015324208, 0.04147455, 0.0037574265, -0.060615774, -0.03361573, 0.019838344, -0.060693406, -0.018339036, 0.009159501, 0.08607168, 0.011462436, -0.037085123, 0.005445017, 0.030060165, -0.10849389, -0.025322905, 0.036016453, -0.0135862725, -0.026568985, -0.008615049, 0.052074272, 0.036686122, 0.0024867975, -0.007613448, 0.051970612, -0.024863843, 0.0013379889, 0.047928587, -0.05230667, -0.0016460764, -0.034524504, -0.018080126, -0.09290793, 0.029157698, 0.066773854, 0.012665494, -0.020368336, 0.03125813, 0.053754527, 0.09590587, -0.05743499, 0.020695677, 0.013268396, 0.031566788, 0.014886277, 0.01741692, -0.042338878, 0.082290605, -0.036997896, -0.07596951, 0.0021828557, 0.08356032, -0.016473489, 0.024583846, 0.0050784843, -0.0004830777, 0.0051761046, 0.11810472, 0.04671067, -0.06318859, 0.01480691, 0.019503366, 0.026478557, -0.07602268, 0.048627123, 0.0053297523, 0.041497983, 0.041904498, -0.0022938573, 0.056858245, 0.038673557, -0.05090575, -0.026984513, -0.029195266, 0.013890276, 0.015655283, 0.028576013, 0.075088724, 0.035697773, 0.057224136, -0.037272476, 0.048545606, 0.038618863, -0.008201358, -0.03499072, -0.0074258726, 0.017316058, -0.01686678, 0.006697862, -0.008154862, 0.0011023225, -0.067572825, 0.048466098, -0.013919293, 0.05907006, -0.004918233, -0.053656615, 0.01824719, -0.025056325, 0.019050919, -0.02749776, 0.0047969446, 0.0037619043, 0.056928508, 0.015800333, 0.00027852034, -0.021058714, -0.044513974, 0.01531700